{"tid":908191,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我成功繼承了廚房佬招雙刀流！","createTime":"2018-11-19T12:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:53:21.000Z","uid":14941,"like":20,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"acd3f25f0de465f77a6611d16dcc1164242728ed","tid":908191,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"今日去酒樓食飯懷疑個大廚有雙刀流<br />\n特登叫左個大廚出黎見我<br />\n<br />\n我一見到個大廚就埋去握手，一掂到佢隻手，就彈左句error msg：immortal object<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢既天命就黎變0，想傳授佢既雙刀流俾反應時間最快既人&mdash; 即係我，去繼承雙刀流既精神<br />\n<br />\n大廚：「睇清楚，我生命最後既一瞬間光輝！星爆！」<br />\n<br />\n我同大廚一齊大喝：「氣！流！斬！」<br />\n<br />\n全場因我地既光輝而喝采，starburst stream的暴風捲起了每場餐枱<br />\n<br />\n靜默。大廚倒下。將手上的捲軸交俾我。周圍的侍應半跪行禮。<br />\n<br />\n我收下卷軸，正式繼承星爆氣流斬。<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"b837f0041c3759fab25fd480dee252b04615fced","tid":908191,"uid":13138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦..."},{"pid":"f246990a68cbf5d375900e5e299c5db7f13985ea","tid":908191,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"近呢兩篇係前傳，我諗大家都好想知我習得星爆氣流斬之前既故事，所以寫俾大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4509edc0d939c15451546b670783dc924e08cae8","tid":908191,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"312986f583086e4ab7fda38b05f7ba05f8696d8b","tid":908191,"uid":28956,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬殺人報左驚"},{"pid":"361ac3f1138589a39a469405365912aeefb52ae6","tid":908191,"uid":39980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"好睇"},{"pid":"ba57a6bad4bcbaf8faf058962b4e924def618c5c","tid":908191,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"咩嚟？古龍定金融？"},{"pid":"8dd6f29c543e4ea0b1ceab2d197646c6289f21cf","t